  "title": "Adam Bailey: My Three Deaths",
  "description": "No matter how many times you die, you only live once! Despite facing death, the award-winning creator of The Life Henri, &amp; Adam Bailey is On Fire, lives on to tell the tales in this personal, funny and poignant show covering all life has to offer. “This puckish urchin of a guy is agreeably user-friendly” - Edmonton Journal",
  "credits": "<strong>Playwright</strong>: Adam Bailey<br/><strong>Director</strong>: Adam Bailey<br/><strong>Cast</strong>: Adam Bailey<br/>",
  "website": "https://stillyourfriend.com",
  "plain_language": "In this heartfelt and funny storytelling show, Adam Bailey shares six true stories: three about facing his own death, and three about the death of loved ones in a single year. Weaving together themes of family, LGBTQ+ identity, and even the supernatural, he tells a touching story of his relationship with his mother that shows how even life’s hardest moments hold humor.",
